<p class = "tutorial-heading">
Creating a Sampler
</p>
<p class = "tutorial-text">
As promised, we also have a sampler! Similarly to the <code>MaxiSynth</code>, you can have up to 8 samplers (each can hold 8 samples). They are stored in the instrument objectâ€™s <code>samplers</code> property. Each will have its own GUI, showing the controls for 4 samples at a time.
</p>

<pre>
